Grammatista Installation Instructions
=====================================

Requirements
------------
Grammatista requires PHP 5.2.2 or later.

External dependencies
---------------------
If you would like to run Grammatista's Unit Tests, you need PHPUnit 3.2 or later installed.

Setting up
----------
To use Grammatista, simply include lib/Grammatista.php, or include lib/Grammatista.class.php and call Grammatista::boostrap().

After that, Grammatista is ready for action. Refer to the documentation to learn how to get started by registering a scanner etc.